{"_path":"/maps/_ai/foundations/core-concepts","_dir":"foundations","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"AI Core Concepts","description":"20个AI核心概念一句话速查","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"ai-core-concepts"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AI Core Concepts"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"20个AI核心概念的一句话总结，涵盖神经网络基础、LLM机制、推理技巧和应用模式。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://blog.algomaster.io/p/20-ai-concepts-explained-simply","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"20 AI Concepts Explained Simply"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"神经网络基础"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"神经网络基础"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"neural-network神经网络"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Neural Network（神经网络）？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"由神经元组成的层级结构，通过逐层转换输入来生成预测。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"transfer-learning迁移学习"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Transfer Learning（迁移学习）？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"复用预训练模型进行新任务，而非从头训练，从而获得强劲的先发优势。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"embeddings嵌入向量"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Embeddings（嵌入向量）？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"捕获语义的向量表示，使语义相似的词在高维向量空间中距离相近。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"attention注意力机制"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Attention（注意力机制）？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"让每个token能够查看输入中的其他所有token，并决定哪些对理解上下文更重要。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"transformer"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Transformer？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"出自论文\"Attention Is All You Need\"的架构，使用堆叠的注意力层并行处理token。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"llm核心机制"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LLM核心机制"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"llm大语言模型"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LLM（大语言模型）？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在数千亿到数万亿token上训练的Transformer，核心能力是预测下一个token。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"tokenization分词"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Tokenization（分词）？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"将文本转换为token（词、子词或字符）的过程，基于固定的词汇表进行映射。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"context-window上下文窗口"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Context Window（上下文窗口）？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"模型一次能处理的最大token数量，相当于LLM的工作记忆容量。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"temperature温度参数"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Temperature（温度参数）？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"控制token选择随机性的参数，0表示确定性输出，1+表示 increasingly random。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"hallucination幻觉"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Hallucination（幻觉）？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LLM生成听起来自信可信但实际上不正确或虚构的内容。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"训练与优化"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"训练与优化"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"fine-tuning微调"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Fine-tuning（微调）？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在特定任务的小数据集上继续训练预训练模型，使其向特定行为方向调整。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"rlhf基于人类反馈的强化学习"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"RLHF（基于人类反馈的强化学习）？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"利用人类对模型回答的排序来训练奖励模型，使LLM输出更有帮助、礼貌且安全。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"lora低秩适配"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LoRA（低秩适配）？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"冻结原始权重，仅添加少量可训练的适配器矩阵，用0.1%到1%的参数实现高效微调。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"quantization量化"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Quantization（量化）？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"将权重精度从32位降至16/8/4位，大幅缩减模型体积并降低内存使用。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"推理技巧"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"推理技巧"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"prompt-engineering提示工程"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Prompt Engineering（提示工程）？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"通过角色设定、 few-shot 示例等技巧精心构造输入，以获得更好的模型输出。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"chain-of-thought思维链"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Chain of Thought（思维链）？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"让模型在给出最终答案前逐步展示推理过程，提高复杂任务的准确性。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"rag检索增强生成"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"RAG（检索增强生成）？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在生成回答前先检索相关文档，使模型输出基于真实、最新的信息。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"vector-database向量数据库"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Vector Database（向量数据库）？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"存储嵌入向量并通过相似度搜索实现\"按语义而非关键词\"检索的数据库。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"应用与生成"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"应用与生成"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"ai-agentsai智能体"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"AI Agents（AI智能体）？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"能够执行操作、做出决策并与外部工具交互的LLM，通过观察-思考-行动循环完成任务。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"diffusion-models扩散模型"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Diffusion Models（扩散模型）？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"通过学习逆转噪声腐蚀过程来生成数据，从随机噪声逐步恢复出结构化信号。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searc